  "decision_conditions": [
    "REASON: The proposed extension of the second floor rear roof terrace and associated screening and ballustrade by reason of inappropriate design, scale, massing, height and prominent location would form an overdominant and visually discordant feature to the rear elevation to the detriment of the character and appearance of the host building and the wider Newington Green Conservation Area.  The proposed development is therefore considered to be contrary to policy 9 of Islington's Core Strategy 2011, Emerging DM policies DM1 & DM3, policies D4 (Designing in context), D11 (Alterations and extensions) D22 (New development) of Islington’s Unitary Development Plan 2002, Newington Green Conservation note, Islington’s Urban Design Guidance 2006 and the NPPF 2012."
